OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,FA nail technician in who is raising
OL,8,Fher prices as part of what's being
OL,9,Fbilled as "National Nail Price
OL,10,FIncrease Day" says it marks a "big
OL,11,Fmoment of solidarity", with some
OL,12,Fworkers earning below the minimum wage
OL,13,Fafter paying their overheads.
OL,15,FMore than 5,000 nail technicians
OL,16,Facross the UK are coming together to
OL,17,Fcollectively raise their prices from
OL,18,Ftoday - Monday, 8 April - as part of
OL,19,Fthe movement.
