OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,FThis is to make a fair wage the Nail
OL,8,FTech Org (NTO) says, as the
OL,9,Forganisation warned its member nail
OL,10,Ftechnicians make on average just under
OL,11,F#7 per hour.
OL,13,FThe minimum wage, also known as
OL,14,FNational Living Wage, increased to
OL,15,F#11.44 per hour for workers over 21
OL,16,Ffrom April 2024.
OL,18,FElsie Tate has been a nail technician
OL,19,Ffor two years and has owned her own
OL,20,Fstudio - Beelsiebub Nailz - for a year.
