OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,FWith rising costs of utilities and
OL,8,Fproducts, she explained the reason for
OL,9,Fthe national price increase is to
OL,10,Fensure all nail technicians are
OL,11,Fearning the minimum wage.
OL,13,FElsie said: "It's really easy to think
OL,14,Fwhen you go into a nail place and you
OL,15,Fpay #40 to think that's going straight
OL,16,Finto the nail tech's pocket.
OL,18,F"But there are so many unseen
OL,19,Foverheads and training and product
OL,20,Freplenishment and all of that, that
OL,21,Fdoesn't get seen.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
