OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,F"It's more common than you realise for
OL,8,Fnail techs to go home with less than
OL,9,Fminimum wage at the end of the day."
OL,11,FElsie said the increase is "relatively
OL,12,Fsmall but in terms of a percentage
OL,13,Fit's quite significant because it
OL,14,Fmeans that I can put aside a pension
OL,15,Fand I can put aside sick pay because
OL,16,FI've not been doing that for the past
OL,17,Fyear, so that's quite an exciting
OL,18,Fthing for me.
OL,20,F"It is a big moment.
