OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,F"It's really important and I'm excited
OL,8,Fthat it's being recognised because
OL,9,Fwhen I first started doing nails, I
OL,10,Fwas really stressed about figuring out
OL,11,Fprices and all of that and the last
OL,12,Fyear it's just been battling 'what
OL,13,Fshould it be? What's a good price?'
OL,14,FBut we've finally kind of made a day
OL,15,Fof it which is good.
