OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,F"The purpose of having a specific day
OL,8,Ffor it is for nail techs, we tend to
OL,9,Fignore the actual expenses of what we
OL,10,Fpay, and I think it's fair to have a
OL,11,Fspecific day for it because otherwise
OL,12,Fa lot of nail techs would put off the
OL,13,Fprice increase or they wouldn't put it
OL,14,Fup as much as they need to and the
OL,15,Fspecific day gives a sense of
OL,16,Fsolidarity which makes it less scary.
