OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,F"A lot of companies are upping the
OL,8,Fprices of their products as well so we
OL,9,Fneed to make sure we stay in line with
OL,10,Fthat so we can keep providing the
OL,11,Fluxury services."
OL,13,FNiamh Crawley is one of Elsie's
OL,14,Fclients and said she is "fine" with
OL,15,Fthe price increase, adding that she
OL,16,Ffelt like what Elsie was previously
OL,17,Fcharging was "too cheap".
OL,19,F"I'm glad she's increasing the
OL,20,Fprices," Niamh said.
