OL,3,CThousands of nail technicians raise
OL,4,Cprices 'in solidarity' to cover unseen
OL,5,Ccosts
OL,7,F"I've been seeing Elsie for a while
OL,8,Fand I remember when she first started
OL,9,Fout, I remember coming away thinking
OL,10,F'gosh she's charging me too low and I
OL,11,Fwould charge more in her position', so
OL,12,FI used to buy her coffees."
OL,14,FShe added: "My sister's a beauty
OL,15,Ftherapist as well and I remember when
OL,16,Fshe was starting out and she was
OL,17,Fgiving student prices and it just
OL,18,Fwasn't covering enough for her and I
OL,19,Ffelt the same for Elsie.
